

Weather App

This repository contains the source code for a weather application that provides real-time weather data.

About

The Weather App allows users to search for current weather conditions based on their location. It utilizes an API to fetch weather data and presents it in a user-friendly interface.

Features

- Real-time weather data retrieval.
- User-friendly interface.
- Responsive design for various devices.

Project Structure

- index.html: Main HTML file for the application.
- App.vue: Vue component for the app's functionality.
- Dockerfile: Contains instructions for building the Docker image.
- Pipfile: Dependency management for Python.

How to Use

1. Clone the repository.
2. Install the required dependencies.
3. Open index.html in your web browser to run the application.

Resources

- API used for weather data: [OpenWeatherMap](https://openweathermap.org/api)

